Package: cMut
Type: Package
Title: Identify Clustered Single Nucleotide Mutations and Link Them to Mutational Patterns
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Alex", "Janse", email = "alex.janse.nl@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: To find clustered single nucleotide variants and 
             link them to mutation patterns, 'cMut' was created. 
             It also provide a simulation function to help determine the enrichment 
             of the found pattern results.
